   236	<threat_model>
   237	## Trust Boundaries
   238	
   239	| Boundary | Description |
   240	|----------|-------------|
   241	| RAW file -> writer | Untrusted/imperfect vendor scan data crosses here; individual scans may be unreadable ("Cannot get scan event for N"). |
   242	| temp file -> STORED zip entry | Internal bytes cross from a seekable temp FileStream into a non-seekable, write-only archive stream. |
   243	
   244	## STRIDE Threat Register
   245	
   246	| Threat ID | Category | Component | Disposition | Mitigation Plan |
   247	|-----------|----------|-----------|-------------|-----------------|
   248	| T-01-01 | Denial of Service | full-facet in-RAM accumulation on multi-GB RAW (v1 OOM) | mitigate | Bounded row-group streaming to seekable temp files (Task 2); peak RSS ~= one buffer per open facet, verified MEM-02 (Task 4). |
   249	| T-01-02 | Tampering | non-seekable sink silently buffers whole facet (looks like streaming, isn't) | mitigate | OpenAsync asserts sink.CanSeek and throws otherwise (Task 1); NonSeekableSinkRejected test; data facets only ever target temp FileStreams. |
   250	| T-01-03 | Tampering | mid-scan throw orphans points / reuses ordinal / poisons precursor-map -> facet-metadata parity break or wrong parent | mitigate | Per-scan all-or-nothing stage-then-commit incl. _precursorScanNumbers (Task 3); ordinal + precursor-map advance only on full success; parity asserted in S4 test; precursor-isolation proved in deterministic unit test. |
   251	| T-01-04 | Denial of Service | multi-GB temp files leaked on a mid-conversion throw | mitigate | try/finally around streaming handles + temp paths; delete all temps in finally (Task 2). |
   252	| T-01-05 | Information Disclosure | footer KV / cv_list lost when accumulators become streamed (regression) | mitigate | Final CustomMetadata set via CloseAsync after all row groups (Task 1/2); shared chrom-data prefix helper runs before BuildMetadataFacet (Task 2); footer KV + cv_list asserted (Tasks 1,2). |
   253	| T-01-06 | Information Disclosure | logical output changes vs v1 (regression) | mitigate | Point layout, schemas, and footer KV unchanged; mzpeak-validate 0/0 + identical-multiset tests + full suite (Tasks 2,4). |
   254	</threat_model>
