**S1-S6**
- S1: RESOLVED - `FinalMetadataSetAfterRowGroups` proves footer round-trip after row groups, and `CloseAsync(finalMetadata)` sets `CustomMetadata` before dispose. [01-01-PLAN.md](/Users/kohlbach/Claude/mzPeak4TRFR/.planning/phases/01-streaming-writer-per-scan-robustness/01-01-PLAN.md:139), [01-01-PLAN.md](/Users/kohlbach/Claude/mzPeak4TRFR/.planning/phases/01-streaming-writer-per-scan-robustness/01-01-PLAN.md:147)
